 and cities where you can also complete quests.<br>The construction mode and first-person mode can be switched seamlessly and depend on each other!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372120/extras/gif_fp.gif?t=1735749809\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372120/extras/arkem_EN_medievalCivil.png?t=1735749809\" /><br>Arkem offers an alternative reality that roughly follows the historical events between 950 and 1300 AD such as the Viking attacks or the first Crusades which you may have to experience - so be prepared. Where do you want your castle to be? Several maps offer you a variety of locations from the Italian Alps to an island in the high north.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372120/extras/arkem_gif_water.gif?t=1735749809\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372120/extras/arkem_banner.png?t=1735749809\" />","developers":["Exovision"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372120/header.jpg?t=1735749809","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257085846,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257085846/movie480.mp4?t=1735749797","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257085846/movie_max.mp4?t=1735749797"},"name":"Arkem Overview